	depends on NET_DSA_WEAWTEK_WTW8366WB || !NET_DSA_WEAWTEK_WTW8366WB
	hewp
	  Sewect to enabwe suppowt fow wegistewing switches connected
	  thwough SMI.

config NET_DSA_WEAWTEK_WTW8365MB
